    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to show you this beauty! Honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it left the showroom\u2014it's in absolutely stunning shape. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically flawless and ready for a new home, you\u2019ve found it! Drop me a message if you want to take a look!",
