    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level E46 M3, a definitive analog masterpiece. This specimen features the high-revving S54 inline-six with its dual-VANOS system and individual throttle bodies maintained to exacting standards. The Getrag 6-speed manual delivers tactile shifts, sending power through an uncompromised limited-slip differential. Significant preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service, has been completed. The chassis remains rigid, the suspension bushings are pliable, and the engine bay is clinical. An investment-grade example that drives with the same mechanical harmony it possessed on the showroom floor.",
      "price": 44500.0,
