      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, currently maintained in superlative condition. This specimen displays an impeccable aesthetic, featuring a flawless exterior finish and a cabin that retains its original showroom integrity. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure performance that meets the most demanding standards of excellence. For the individual seeking a vehicle of unrivaled pedigree and meticulous preservation, this offering represents an absolute benchmark in its class.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
